{"tid":49568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉超市偷234元貨物　否認控罪1月審理","createTime":"2016-12-21T20:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T08:14:45.000Z","uid":62257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5be065e149c061ac0b2d7f38fc79039691e6ff5","tid":49568,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/800149/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F800149%2F&d=smd8PAPZq11A2qEuW46VUBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=d03c4708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F800149%2F&h=2f923b12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/800149/</a><br />\n休班女警黃偉芬（49歲）涉嫌於今年10月在秀茂坪商場的一間超市偷竊總值234元的貨物，她否認一項盜竊罪，原定今日在觀塘法院開審，惟證人眾多，裁判官黃雅茵恐怕一天未必可完成，認為需排2天審期，故將案件轉交主任裁判官重新排期。主任裁判官練錦鴻接案後質疑「審唔完唔係理由，咩官呀」，最後亦只排期一天，稱未能完成便繼續順延，案件明年1月4日開審。 <br />\n<br />\n控辯雙方會傳召7名證人。辯方庭上稱，被告在涉案前曾服食傷風藥及咳藥水，或受藥物影響，並無意圖偷竊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於今年10月10日，在秀茂坪商場一樓的惠康超級市場內，涉偷竊兩盒防蚊貼、一樽驅蚊噴霧、一樽XO醬及兩盒喉片，總值234元。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：潘琪慧"},{"pid":"728a9bf053455e0f1246fa599735a12d01819271","tid":49568,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13d392070d1093c21c48e6a5cd0382380803d2bd","tid":49568,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"休班警全盛時期"},{"pid":"7856176181a96dfb021b9d874b026d9fa924c7b6","tid":49568,"uid":67686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T20:12:18.000Z","msg":"佢點會知法犯法，一定係唔記得比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">入去坐返10年8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1fff41113d24f744d269a3b66a1b2e4e18c4793b","tid":49568,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12